original: Ljungqvist, Anders Johan Gustaf, komminister, Rydöbruk, f. 20/1/91 i Halmstad av Carl L. o. Johanna An-dersdotter. G. 30 m. Greta Hjorth. Ad :dtr: Helena Orvokki Laatikainen. — Stud:ex. i Halmstad 11, fil. kand. i Lund 18, teol. kand., prakt. teol. prov o. prästv. f. Växjö ’stift 24. Tjg. s. v. pastor i Berga, Forsheda o. Bur-seryd samt s. v. kommin. i Långaryd, vakanskommin. i Burseryd 27-29, kommin. i Långaryd (Rydöbruk) 28, tilltr. 30. Vik. adj. v. Halmstads h. a. 1. 22, v. realsk. i Varberg 24. Insp. f. Rydöbruks föreläsn :fören.
translated: Ljungqvist, Anders Johan Gustaf, curate, Rydöbruk, b. 20/1/91 in Halmstad to Carl L. and Johanna Andersdotter. Married on 30th, with Greta Hjorth. Children: daughter Helena Orvokki Laatikainen. — Completed high school in Halmstad in 1911, B.A. in Lund in 1918, completed theological studies, practical theological examinations and ordained as a priest in Växjö diocese in 1924. Currently serving as a pastor in Berga, Forsheda, and Burseryd, as well as curate in Långaryd. Previously served as a temporary curate in Burseryd from 1927 to 1929, and became curate in Långaryd (Rydöbruk) in 1928, assumed duty in 1930. Also served as temporary vicar in Halmstads h. a. 1. in 1922, and as a teacher at Varberg secondary school in 1924. Inspected for Rydöbruk's lecture association.
